<aside class="sidebar">

    <section>
      
      <h2>AMAZON QUICK SEARCH</h2>
      <section data-group="modal-group">
        <div class="container">
          <a href="#" class="image fit"><img src="https://pmcvariety.files.wordpress.com/2018/01/amazon-logo.jpg?w=1000" alt=""></a>
          <p>Amazon offers thousands of great deals, but finding the best deal through endless pages might make you crazy. It offers a quick way to find the best deals on Amazon.</p>
          <a class="button btn-px open-modal" data-modal="modal">Quick Search</a>
          <div class="modal-wrapper" data-wrapper="modal-wrapper-large">
           <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-intro">
             <h2>Quick way to find the best deals</h2>
